Package com.epoch.genericQTypes

Classes for holding and analyzing responses to simple response types such as rank, multiple choice, number, and table.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Choice
    Holds a response to a multiple-choice or fill-blank question.
    ChooseExplain
    Holds a response to a choose-and-explain question.
    ClickImage
    Holds a response to a clickable image question.
    Logic
    Class for the logical statements question type.
    Numeric
    Holds a response to a numerical question.
    Rank
    Holds a response to a rank or numbering question.
    TableQ
    Class for the complete-the-table question type.
